{
  "stem": "9503.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just very purposefully, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sort of, you know, in a-- in a childlike way, put a line under it and said, that goes in the box, and we go from now.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The only thing-- and again, that-- that comes back under-- under some of the disillusionments-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] one of my first trips when we came back from-- from the camps was to find out where these twins were who had my doll.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went to their apartment and I said, hi, I'm here for my doll.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I got this funny look, which, to this day, I don't quite explain or can't or don't want to, and they don't have the doll.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And maybe this doll was too ugly to bring back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they had promised me that they'd bring back the doll, and they didn't.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I started sort of questioning all of a sudden, how come they were allowed to stay in this camp with my doll, you know, where all the children had to leave?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I got an explanation from either my uncle or from my mother that the father was involved with making up the lists of the people who were going to go on transport.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, that's one job that is essential.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You don't find too many volunteers for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that-- that came much later, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At the time, I only remember that they hadn't brought my doll back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I do remember that everybody was searching frantically for family members.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, there was this constant, if somebody came back, oh, did you know my relative?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This seemed to be going on among the grown-ups.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
